ClientSideProviderFactoryCallback Delegate

Definition

Represents the method that creates a client-side UI Automation provider for a window.

In this Article

public delegate System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IRawElementProviderSimple ClientSideProviderFactoryCallback(IntPtr hwnd, int idChild, int idObject);
Inheritance
Object
Delegate
ClientSideProviderFactoryCallback

Examples

For example code, see Create a Client-Side UI Automation Provider.
